{"tid":238414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夜歸女被搶手袋 論盡賊疑留低銀包","createTime":"2017-05-11T04:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T04:20:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de89900150c25154b08ad761c6f0f5fc277993b2","tid":238414,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170511/large/1494450059_ef8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170511%2Flarge%2F1494450059_ef8d.jpg&h=8a23b68f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170511/large/1494474540_9da6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170511%2Flarge%2F1494474540_9da6.jpg&h=1c90a392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【11：49更新】有商舖cctv拍得賊人容貌，當時賊人戴口罩，拿着搶來的手袋逃走。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨3時許，一名37歲姓王女子，行經旺角大南街86號對開，被一名戴口罩賊人從後搶去手袋，內有7,000港元、500元人民幣、一部值3,000元手機及約值33,000的首飾。賊人得手後走過對面馬路，穿過後巷經荔枝角大南街休憩處逃跑。女事主窮追約30米，目送賊人往白楊街方向逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n女事主其後向途人借電話報警，警方到場調查，在附近撿獲一個口罩。同時，另有一名途人，在大南街一店舖對開撿獲一個銀包，內有一名男子的身份證及信用卡，交由警方處理。警方不排除是賊人掉下，撿走調查。案中女事主沒有受傷返警署助查。<br />\n<br />\n有商舖門外的閉路電視拍得賊人戴口罩，穿白色長袖衫、深色長褲，拿著手袋匆匆由對面馬路跑過洗衣店，最後往白楊街方向逃去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56678315&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56678315%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1b21784c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56678315%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&h=5feb86cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56678315&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511</a>"},{"pid":"d44dd68d4970f939b50ff5d51aac00c57fb9d3d5","tid":238414,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:05:48.000Z","msg":"又黎"},{"pid":"1444eaeec5f37d6b6f35716765840e2c82d40e10","tid":238414,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c19ee84222efed4ff0bc635417c8fa6b254d195e","tid":238414,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"帶咁多錢係身 仲唔係g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc9130f961104e276f4964d1b7ba17a928a36b9","tid":238414,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶咁多錢係身 仲唔係g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係似🐔多啲喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff4c2d39ac49480593f4df7048199212c5982fc","tid":238414,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:10:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶咁多錢係身 仲唔係g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日做10單生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e64033eedcd7442e0ca555350fbb6d8db9bcdcf","tid":238414,"uid":101390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"臭g 做完收工返歸比人打劫"}]}